### 🔟 Review & Iterate
```bash
# Address review comments
# Keep commits clean
git commit -m "feat(intake): address review feedback"

# Re-run affected checks
nx affected:test --base=origin/main
```

### 1️⃣1️⃣ Staging Deploy (Flag OFF)
```bash
# Deploy with flag OFF
FEATURE_<NAME>_ENABLED=false npm run deploy:staging

# Run post-deploy smoke
npm run test:smoke:staging

# Enable for internal testing
FEATURE_<NAME>_ENABLED=true npm run test:e2e:staging

# Monitor logs/metrics
tail -f logs/staging.log | grep "feature_x"
```

### 1️⃣2️⃣ Production Rollout
```typescript
// Progressive flag ramp
const rolloutSchedule = {
  day1: { percentage: 1, cohort: 'internal' },
  day2: { percentage: 10, cohort: 'beta_users' },
  day3: { percentage: 50, cohort: 'all_users' },
  day4: { percentage: 100, cohort: 'all_users' }
};

// Monitor KPIs
const monitoring = {
  errorRate: '< 0.1%',
  latencyP95: '< 500ms',
  businessMetric: 'conversion_rate'
};
```

### 1️⃣3️⃣ Finish & Cleanup
```bash
# Update documentation
npm run docs:generate

# Update CHANGELOG
echo "### Added
- Feature X: Description" >> CHANGELOG.md

# Remove temporary code
git grep "TODO(feature_x)" | xargs -I {} sed -i '' 's/TODO(feature_x)//' {}

# Close ticket
gh issue close <issue-number> --comment "Feature shipped successfully"
```

